casebody.data:
No. 10-449. Edward F. Richards, Petitioner v. Hewlett-Packard Corporation, fka Compaq, fka Digital Equipment Corporation, et al. 562 U.S. 1102, 131 S. Ct. 798,

178 L. Ed. 2d 545,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 9482. December 6, 2010.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the First Circuit denied.

The Chief Justice took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 592 F.3d 232.
